trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Message"> </xref>，代表要處理訊息的參考所傳遞。

trans-unit.source: The possible values are WM_KEYDOWN, WM_SYSKEYDOWN, WM_CHAR, and WM_SYSCHAR.

trans-unit.source: Processes a dialog key if the WebBrowser ActiveX control does not process it.
trans-unit.target: 如果 WebBrowser ActiveX 控制項不會處理會處理對話方塊按鍵。

trans-unit.source: This method is called during message preprocessing to handle dialog characters, such as TAB, RETURN, ESCAPE, and arrow keys.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫這個方法是在處理對話方塊字元，例如索引標籤、 RETURN、 逸出及方向鍵前置處理的訊息。

trans-unit.source: This method is called only if the WebBrowser ActiveX control does not process the key.
trans-unit.target: WebBrowser ActiveX 控制項不會處理索引鍵時，才會呼叫這個方法。

trans-unit.source: In this case, this method delegates the call to the base <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ProcessDialogKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: 在此情況下，這個方法會委派呼叫基底<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ProcessDialogKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName>方法。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ProcessDialogKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Keys"></xref> values that represents the key to process.
trans-unit.target: 其中一個<xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Keys"></xref>值，表示要處理的按鍵。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the key was processed by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserBase"></xref>; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
